      • getCurrentVersion

        public static int getCurrentVersion()
        This method will return the closest or exact version number of the current server. Only contains versions people will reasonably use and will fail with an exception, when the target version is before 1.12.2. (Assuming no one will update 1.8 items to 1.11, if so, provide the version numbers to the converter method directly)
